# identify subclasses at each clustering resolution

subclass.idx <- list()

subclass.idx$type$Pvalb <- c("Pvalb_A", "Pvalb_B", "Pvalb_C", "Pvalb_D")
subclass.idx$type$Sst <- c("Sst_A", "Sst_B", "Sst_C", "Sst_D", "Sst_E")
subclass.idx$type$Vip <- c("Vip_A", "Vip_B", "Vip_C")

subclass.idx$type$Frem1 <- c("Frem1")
subclass.idx$type$Stac <- c("Stac")

obj.mouse.gabaergic <- SubclassByIdent(obj.mouse.gabaergic, subclass.idx)
